  -Stakeholder Type is Identified
    +As a user
  -Outcome is Described
    +I want a friendly interface
  -Rational is Explicit
    +so that I can easily use this product.
    
    
Acceptance Criteria:
-Working user interface exists that is available to users.
-User interface is user-friendly.
